body:
And you be like, asking them to sit with you to listen to your LoL stories like:

&quot;Back in my days, we used to have Mana pots...&quot;
&quot;OH WOW, RLLY GRANDPA?? THATS CRAZY!!&quot;
&quot;Ah yes, crazy indeed. Ahhh missed the good ol times.....&quot;


So what would your first LoL storytime to your grandkids be like?
